<Verbatim PAsource="" >"We all have to live for the rest of our lives with the knowledge of what he did and what really happened."</Verbatim>


<Verbatim PAsource="" >Sentencing Hobbs, who had refused to undergo psychiatric analysis, </Verbatim>
